              "name": "Character Guide pg. 122",
              "type": "link"
            },
            "name": "Character Guide",
            "page": 122,
            "type": "source"
          }
        ],
        "text": "For centuries, the nation of Lastwall stood as a bulwark against the orcs of Belkzen and the lingering threat of the Whispering Tyrant. But when the Whispering Tyrant escaped his prison, he brought to his enemies in Lastwall a devastating apocalypse. Now Lastwall is destroyed, and the knights who once served there are without a home. In its absence, they have formed a ragtag group known as the Knights of Lastwall, and they carry on their charge to stand against the undead legions of the Whispering Tyrant wherever their skills are needed.",
        "type": "monster_family"
      },
